::KitKat::

She pushed the body off her and got up.  The acid burned in her other 
shoulder.  She looked at Drill bit.  She felt pain surge through her 
body.  She looked at Drillbit and then turned to look at Stingtra and 
the others.  She felt the pain again.  She also felt tired and 
drained.  She walked over to the tree and sat down at it's base.  She 
leaned back and rested.  She didn't have much energy left to fight 
with.  With all the damage and loss of mech fluid, she would need 
help soon.  But she had to stay with her leader.
